channel.title: [422] Changing window title
channel.description:
Yes I know this is very simple, I've only spent 10 mins on new client so far and I'm trying to find things which I can post which no one else has posted :p
Open Applet_Sub1.java
Find
[code] Class58_Sub6.aFrame1957.setTitle("Jagex"); [/code]
And change Jagex to whatever you want :D
